{
  "stem": "1222.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Millions-- I think it was 18 million people totally, not just the Jews-- was 6 million-- but they lost another 12 million, between the Russians and the-- you know, the Ukrainians, altogether.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Not talking about deaths.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We saw ourselves, in the forest, so many dead people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Heads, feet.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It's hard to believe it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Not just Jews-- they used to kill each other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They used to have three kinds of partisans, the Ukrainians.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They used to be [NON-ENGLISH], [NON-ENGLISH], and [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "That was all Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The [NON-ENGLISH] said like that, that the Jews could be alive.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Germans could be alive, but they have to be slaves.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The [NON-ENGLISH] said like the Germans, .",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "No nation should be alive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They should have some state of Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "That's what they're having right now.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The-- the [NON-ENGLISH] said, yes, the Jews could be alive, and they were good, and we've got to save them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there used to be many times two brothers-- they were two different parties-- they used to kill each other.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How did they kill them?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "With knives, whatever they had.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, that was a lot of-- that was going on, we didn't know who to make-- you had to be very, very fast-- fast-thinking-- because you never know.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Every second, the bullet goes so fast, you'll be killed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And if you don't take chances, you can't be survive, because how will you steal food?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How will you-- I mean, summertime was a cinch because we had a lot of food there growing, and there used to be the heads for the cabbage that we used to pick them up and chew them.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We used to eat, many times, from that dead horse.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We used to come around-- anything which was biting, what you eat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You try to do it.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
